text: Willy Van Den Bossche is an archer from Belgium. Bossche competed at the 1980 Summer Olympics and the 1984 Summer Olympics.Willy VAN DEN BOSSCHE He was born on 22 January 1949.Willy Van Den Bossche == References == Category:1949 births Category:Living people Category:Belgian archers Category:Olympians for Belgium
